{"tid":2265014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［律政司提上訴呀！］社工陳虹秀首先被律政司提出上訴","createTime":"2020-10-31T05:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T05:58:45.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"81a0b7e069fc132914a7c718b5350ca59ca2214f","tid":2265014,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T05:55:45.000Z","msg":"事隔14個月，8.31灣仔暴動案今日終有裁決，八名被告全部獲判無罪。其中被控暴動的社工陳虹秀，早在今年9月審訊中途便因案件表面證供不成立，毋須答辯，當庭釋放。不過，律政司未待法官頒下裁決理由，便急急表明將會就此以案件呈述方式提出上訴。屆時若上訴庭接納律政司申請，便須推翻裁決，重新審訊，甚至判其有罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/XGSU3SMCGVD5BCBTH3HAR4J3YI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FXGSU3SMCGVD5BCBTH3HAR4J3YI%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0UsakxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=022fd2cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FXGSU3SMCGVD5BCBTH3HAR4J3YI%2F&h=51edf564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/XGSU3SMCGVD5BCBTH3HAR4J3YI/</a>"},{"pid":"329ce902114363b631337f1c7214d5b8d22abf25","tid":2265014,"uid":373455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T05:58:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}